ima: Streamlining African Car Market","slug":"carima-streamlining-african-car-market","date":"2024-03-23T01:57:34","agoDate":"a day ago","thumbnail":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Pix-3.jpeg","thumbnail_small":"","thumbnail_medium":"","thumbnail_full":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Pix-3.jpeg","excerpt":"","author":null,"category":null,"url":"/index.php/2024/03/23/carima-streamlining-african-car-market"},{"title":"Caloha’s 3-day Display of Chery at  Ikeja City Mall Captivates Customers","slug":"calohas-3-day-display-of-chery-at-ikeja-city-mall-captivates-customers","date":"2024-03-23T01:54:48","agoDate":"a day ago","thumbnail":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Page-1-Pic-1-Carloha.jpeg","thumbnail_small":"","thumbnail_medium":"","thumbnail_full":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Page-1-Pic-1-Carloha.jpeg","excerpt":"","author":null,"category":null,"url":"/index.php/2024/03/23/calohas-3-day-display-of-chery-at-ikeja-city-mall-captivates-customers"},{"title":"Toyota Nigeria Presents 9 School Children for Another Global Dream Car Art Contest","slug":"toyota-nigeria-presents-9-school-children-for-another-global-dream-car-art-contest","date":"2024-03-23T01:46:42","agoDate":"a day ago","thumbnail":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Screenshot_20240323-112049.jpg","thumbnail_small":"","thumbnail_medium":"","thumbnail_full":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Screenshot_20240323-112049.jpg","excerpt":"","author":null,"category":null,"url":"/index.php/2024/03/23/toyota-nigeria-presents-9-school-children-for-another-global-dream-car-art-contest"},{"title":"Weststar Unveils All-new Mercedes-Benz E-Class Saloon","slug":"weststar-unveils-all-new-mercedes-benz-e-class-saloon","date":"2024-03-23T01:35:21","agoDate":"a day ago","thumbnail":"https://global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Pix-4-Mercede